name: Black God Tee
description: There is one Navajo legend about Black God and the Pleiades. It begins with Black God, who carries a fawn skin pouch containing unnamed star crystals. Black God is solely responsible for “beautifying the ‘dark upper’ or sky” . He then decorates the sky in an orderly way with the prominent and familiar constellations. Their light comes from a special ignite-star he provides from his own Fire. Then he sprinkles the sky with the Milky Way.The BLACK-GOD wouldn't let anyone touch the pouch but COYOTE snatched it anyway. He tasted the crystals inside, didn't like the flavor and spat them into the face of the Black God, who snatched the pouch back. But there was nothing left but dust, which he shook out, forming the Milky Way. Thus creating the mask of the Black God.

name: Anime Tee
description: The Anime Tee is a small design that signifies the bond between the founders of Creed Co. The front carries the letter face with the word creed(x2) in kanji. On the back "anime" is written vertically in Kanji, followed by the print of the"Hidden leaf" on the sleeve. Often times within anime one hears them speak highly of their admiration towards their comrades. This tee highlights the bonds shared and developed through friendship.

name: Coexistence Tee
description: Creed Co.'s "Coexistence Tee" simply highlights and praises the major religious groups today in our society. The back features a circular patch like print that collectively display influences of Christianity, Judaism, and Muslim. Promoting peace on a canvas of 100% cotton. Made in USA.

name: Shanti tee
description: Creed Co.'s "Shanti tee" features an outline of the Buddhist prophet Buddha with the word shanti written in Sanskrit. Shanti by definition means peace and tranquility which aids in Creed Co's mission to promote positive messages to young Visionaries. The back features a "shanti 00" jersey style print layout. 100% cotton, Made in USA.
